        unlock: "Character Reaches Lv. 20",
        text: "Rebecca does not care how others view her. She only cares about two things.\nFirst, to craft the most charming fragrance infused with love, and then sell it to infatuated individuals to help them find love.\nSecond, to find her destined one.",
