        charId: 5101,
        name: "Secret: Ⅳ",
        unlock: "Character Reaches Lv. 50",
        text: "Truffle loathes war. At the slightest hint of it, she and Filbert immediately begin stockpiling food, not only for their fellow townsfolk but also for refugees who might seek sanctuary from their shattered lives.",
