        name: "Secret: Ⅳ",
        unlock: "Character Reaches Lv. 60",
        text: "\"Those who treat knowledge as a mere stepping stone to power will never acquire truths.\"\nThat was the only comment Sibylle's revered mentor — the chief alchemist — left on her graduation certificate, despite her having graduated as the top student. The room was steeped in an eerie silence, filled only with the sound of Sibylle's measured, restrained breathing.",
