        charId: 3103,
        name: "Witness: Ⅱ",
        unlock: "Character Reaches Lv. 30",
        text: "Yale had always despised the smell of hospitals, the harsh scent of disinfectant, and the overpowering odour emanating from bottles of potions and drugs. Even the herbal fragrances worn by pharmacists from Huaxu made him instinctively want to keep his distance, despite knowing it was rather rude. These smells brought back memories of the Alchemy Academy — the lingering scent of Yale's past nightmares.",
