        text: "Fina was born into an unconventional family, with a Charon father and a Sola mother — a rare occurrence in Hyperborea for obvious reasons.\nHer parents were clandestine devotees of the Great Nine of Elysium, practising a faith that preached indistinguishable equality between Solas and Charons, despite their disparate physical appearances and abilities. However, such beliefs were strictly prohibited in Hyperborea. Fina's father was eventually apprehended and executed for his convictions. In a final act of protection, he claimed sole responsibility for hiding the forbidden Elysian scriptures found in their home, hoping to shield his wife and daughter from persecution.",
