        text: "Under the weight of survival, Rhythm has grown dulled — to pain, to exhaustion, even to her own limits. And she doesn't even realise it. Once, she worked eight straight hours in a high-heat zone — the kind that would knock an ordinary human unconscious in ten minutes. And when she emerged, unharmed and calm as ever, even those among her comrades who had long harboured prejudice against the Charon found themselves seeing her differently — with a flicker of respect, and a shadow of fear.",
