        charId: 1502,
        name: "Anecdote: Ⅰ",
        unlock: "Character Reaches Lv. 20",
        text: "According to the ancient legends of the Charon, the souls of the departed are destined to return to the Misty Sea. To honour this belief, the Charon have long observed the tradition of water burials.\nWhen night falls and the moonlight glimmers on the surface of the water, the bones or cherished keepsakes of the dead are placed upon small boats. Then, the Ferrywoman begins the Dance of Departure — a solemn rite said to guide the wandering souls back home, towards the Misty Sea.",
