        text: "Back in her Academy days, Daphne displayed an unusual sensitivity to the wars. Whenever a battle broke out, she would find a way to obtain the list of the fallen.\n \nEach time, she scanned it in anxious silence for one particular name — and each time, let out the faintest sigh of relief when it was not there.\n \nBut now... she no longer needs to look.",
