        id: 23011,
        charId: 1501,
        name: "Secret: Ⅰ",
        unlock: "Character Reaches Lv. 20",
        text: "The young Lisbell, having drawn the sacred sword Samael, was duly named candidate for Patience among the Seven Virtues of the Elysian Church.\n \nShe did not at once assume the vacant seat of Patience — not merely because her years were too tender for so great a burden, but more so because Samael, from that moment on, never again deigned to answer her.\n \nThus, to rouse the slumbering spirit within the sacred blade, Lisbell set forth upon her path of cultivation.",
